<item>
            <title>[CLI-141] CLI Option reports arguments incorrectly on toString()</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CLI-141</link>
                <project id="12310463" key="CLI">Commons CLI</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The Option class contains some logic around the &quot;hasArg&quot; boolean that seems to be cruft and no longer works correctly. There is no need for this boolean anymore and its only usage could be replaced with hasArg() / hasArgs() calls.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12375421">CLI-141</key>
            <summary>CLI Option reports arguments incorrectly on toString()</summary>
